    "summary": "Delayed gastric emptying without mechanical obstruction, causing nausea, vomiting, early satiety, and bloating",
    "key_points": [
      "Delayed gastric emptying without obstruction",
      "Most common cause is diabetes mellitus",
      "Gastric emptying study confirms diagnosis",
      "Symptoms: nausea, vomiting, early satiety, bloating",
      "Treatment: dietary modification, prokinetics, gastric electrical stimulation"
    ],
