      "key_insight": "Key concepts in Gastroparesis management.",
      "technical_details": "Impaired gastric motility from neuropathy (diabetic autonomic neuropathy), post-surgical vagal injury, or idiopathic causes leads to delayed emptying. Symptoms result from food retention and gastric distension."
